---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
import { BRAND } from "../lib/brand";
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<Base
  title={`Privacy policy | ${BRAND.name}`}
  description="How we collect, use, and protect your personal data at Harmony Threads."
>
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-5 md:px-8 py-16">
    <nav class="text-xs text-bone/40 mb-4">
      <a href="/" class="hover:text-rust">Home</a> <span class="mx-2">/</span> <span>Privacy</span>
    </nav>
    <h1 class="font-display text-5xl">Privacy policy</h1>
    <p class="mt-2 text-bone/50">Last updated 20 April {year}.</p>
    <div class="mt-10 space-y-5 text-bone/80 leading-relaxed">
      <p>We collect the minimum personal data needed to run the shop: your email, shipping address, and order history. Payment details are handled entirely by Stripe — we never see or store your card number.</p>
      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl mt-8">What we collect</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
        <li>Name, email, phone, shipping address (when you place an order).</li>
        <li>Email only (if you subscribe to the newsletter).</li>
        <li>Anonymous analytics (page views, approximate country). No identifying ad tracking.</li>
      </ul>
      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl mt-8">How we use it</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
        <li>To fulfil your orders and send transactional email (receipts, shipping notifications).</li>
        <li>To send the occasional newsletter — you can unsubscribe with one click.</li>
        <li>To improve the Site — never sold, never shared with advertisers.</li>
      </ul>
      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl mt-8">Your rights</h2>
      <p>Under UK GDPR you can request a copy of your data, ask us to correct it, or have it deleted. Email <a href={`mailto:${BRAND.email}`} class="underline hover:text-rust">{BRAND.email}</a> and we'll handle it within 30 days.</p>
      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl mt-8">Cookies</h2>
      <p>We use essential cookies only — cart contents, session info. No ad or tracking cookies.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
